item.title: Hanging around outside Whole Foods in Austin
item.dc:creator: Lloyd Davis
item.content:encoded: Just found this snippet - notable mostly for the grackle soundtrack. As it happens I was waiting for @irinaslutsky whom I'd never met before to come along and pick me up in a taxi. Â Much better than another night when I stood on the opposite corner trying to hail a cab and got pooped on by the birds in the trees above.
